<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Podcast Engine — TNHIQ Admin</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif; max-width: 1100px; margin: 1rem auto; padding: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; color: #222; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: .25rem; }
    .lead { color: #666; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .config { padding: .75rem 1rem; background: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: .9rem; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: .9rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    th, td { padding: .5rem .75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; }
    th { background: #fafafa; font-weight: 600; }
    code { background: #f5f5f5; padding: .1rem .4rem; border-radius: 3px; font-size: .85rem; }
    .empty { padding: 2rem; text-align: center; color: #888; }
    a { color: #25aae2; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Podcast Engine</h1>
  <p class="lead">RSS-driven episode ingestion to community threads.</p>

  <div class="config">
    <strong>RSS URL:</strong> <%= @rss_url.present? ? @rss_url : "<em>not configured — set tnhiq_podcast_rss_url</em>".html_safe %><br>
    <strong>Default category:</strong> <code><%= SiteSetting.tnhiq_podcast_default_category %></code> ·
    <strong>Pin days:</strong> <%= SiteSetting.tnhiq_podcast_pin_days %> ·
    <strong>Max per poll:</strong> <%= SiteSetting.tnhiq_podcast_max_per_poll %>
  </div>

  <p>
    POST to <code>/admin/plugins/tnhiq-podcast/poll-now</code> to trigger an immediate poll.<br>
    POST to <code>/admin/plugins/tnhiq-podcast/ingest-one</code> with a JSON body to ingest a single episode for testing.
  </p>

  <h2 style="margin-top:1.5rem;font-size:1.15rem">Recently ingested</h2>

  <% if @episodes.empty? %>
    <div class="empty">No episodes ingested yet.</div>
  <% else %>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Ingested</th>
          <th>Episode</th>
          <th>Title</th>
          <th>Topic</th>
          <th>Category</th>
          <th>GUID</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% @episodes.each do |ep| %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= ep.created_at.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M") %></td>
            <td><%= ep.episode_number.presence || "—" %></td>
            <td><%= ep.title %></td>
            <td>
              <% if ep.topic_id %>
                <a href="/t/<%= ep.topic_id %>" target="_blank">#<%= ep.topic_id %></a>
              <% else %>—<% end %>
            </td>
            <td><code><%= ep.category_id %></code></td>
            <td><code><%= ep.guid.truncate(40) %></code></td>
          </tr>
        <% end %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  <% end %>
</body>
</html>
